<item>
            <title>[FLINK-22413] Hide Checkpointing page in the UI for batch jobs</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-22413</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This is a follow up to &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/flink/commit/8dca9fa852c72984ac873eae9a96bbd739e502f3#commitcomment-49744255&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/flink/commit/8dca9fa852c72984ac873eae9a96bbd739e502f3#commitcomment-49744255&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Batch jobs don&apos;t need a Checkpointing page, because there is no information for these jobs available there.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
